data.title: Francoise Rosay
data.meta_description: Explore the filmography of Francoise Rosay on Rotten Tomatoes! Discover ratings, reviews, and more. Click for details!
data.text:
Highest Rated: 100% Carnival in Flanders (1935)

Lowest Rated: 60% The Sound and the Fury (1959)

Birthday: Apr 19, 1891

Birthplace: Paris, France

Prolific, charismatic character actress from the French stage who turned her attention to film following her marriage to director Jacques Feyder in 1917. Rosay appeared in over 100 international films during a sixty-year career.

Highest rated movies

100% Carnival in Flanders

86% The 13th Letter
